name: less-learn
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "less-learn" %}
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/less-learn-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ce100c4df334a2da687ecd22086c237c353ac2d5d75139f59cfb4704083bd546

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - numpy >=1.21.5
    - python >=3.6
    - scikit-learn >=1.0.1

test:
  imports:
    - less
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/sibirbil/LESS
  summary: Learning with Subset Stacking
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - sibirbil
